<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />I take refuge in Yahweh;</para>

<para style="q1">how will you say to me,</para>

<para style="q1">"Flee like a bird to the mountain"?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />For see! The wicked prepare their bows.</para>

<para style="q1">They make ready their arrows on the strings</para>

<para style="q1">to shoot in the darkness at the upright in heart.</para>
